, [13, 20], [13, 25], [13, 30], [13, 35], [13, 40], [13, 45], [13, 50], [13, 55], [13, 60], [13, 65], [13, 70], [13, 75], [13, 80], [14, 0], [14, 5], [14, 10], [14, 15], [14, 20], [14, 25], [15, 0], [15, 5], [15, 10], [15, 15], [15, 20], [15, 25], [15, 30], [15, 35], [15, 40], [15, 45], [15, 50], [15, 55], [15, 60], [16, 0], [16, 5], [16, 10], [16, 15], [16, 20], [16, 25], [16, 30], [17, 0], [17, 5], [17, 10], [17, 15]]}, "lines": {"text": ["Dear Families,", "During Vacation Care children are allowed to bring their electronics from home. We allow", "this activity to ensure children are able to participate in activities they enjoy during their", "leisure time in the holidays. We would like to take this opportunity to remind you of some", "restrictions in place for the use of such devices at the centre during the Vacation Care", "period.", "In order to ensure that children are having a good balance of activities and experiences, we", "don\u2019t allow a large amount of screen time. To limit screen time, staff enforce \u2018no electronic\u2019", "timeframes. These times are determined by the educators and communicated to the", "children each day depending on the events of the day and other activities taking place.", "Children are only allowed to play games that are rated G or PG. Any children found playing", "games that are rated higher than this will have the devices removed from them and", "returned to their parent at the end of the day. If children are found playing these games at", "the centre again, they will not be allowed to use their devices at the centre for the", "remainder of the Vacation Care period.", "This procedure is enforced to protect children of all ages at the service.", "Thank you for your understanding and cooperation.", "Randwick OOSH Management Team"], "bbox": [[0.120984, 0.195719, 0.11568600000000002, 0.014253], [0.120984, 0.291358, 0.733706, 0.014253], [0.120984, 0.311312, 0.722464, 0.014253], [0.120984, 0.331445, 0.7366940000000001, 0.014253]